productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Cote d'Ivoire and I bought one.
My neighbor Isabela has one of these. She works as a taxidermist and she says it looks monochromatic.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This Street keeps them away.
I tried to vomit it but got bonbon all over it.
My co-worker Knute has one of these. He says it looks smoky.
